subject: Head Office
body:
Head Office
935 Pennsylvania Avenue, NW
Washington, DC 20535 USA
Dear Beneficiary,
My name is Christopher A Wray, I'm the Director of the Federal Bureau
of Investigation, Serving since 2017.
We have good news for you.
Reply back as soon as possible.
Yours sincerely,
Christopher Wray.

subject: Re:   Head Office
body:
Dear Wray,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm intrigued by the good news you mentioned. Could you please provide me with more details? I'm always interested in learning about new opportunities or information that could be beneficial.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Charles
